data.description: Classic Single level Santa Rosa home in a great neighborhood. The home may need some work but it is on a double (15000 sq ft) lot and has some outbuildings. Newer roof. Original oak hardwood floors in some rooms. There is a driveway on both the East and West side of the home for truck / tractor access or parking.
